fileSamples.statement:
(⋃₁t ∈ threads_set G' \₁ eq tid_init, eq (ta_propagate t))
≡₁ (⋃₁t ∈ threads_set G \₁ eq tid_init, eq (ta_propagate t)).

eq ta_cover <*> (acts_set G' \₁ (fun a : actid => is_init a))
∪₁ (eq ta_issue ∪₁ eq ta_reserve ∪₁ is_ta_propagate_to_G G') <*>
   ((acts_set G' \₁ (fun a : actid => is_init a))
    ∩₁ (fun a : actid => is_w (lab G') a))
≡₁ eq ta_cover <*> (acts_set G \₁ (fun a : actid => is_init a))
   ∪₁ (eq ta_issue ∪₁ eq ta_reserve ∪₁ is_ta_propagate_to_G G) <*>
      ((acts_set G \₁ (fun a : actid => is_init a))
       ∩₁ (fun a : actid => is_w (lab G) a)).
fileSamples.proofString:
rewrite EQACTS.
rewrite is_ta_propagate_to_G_more.
now rewrite EQW.
